title: Donkey of the Day - "Dental Chip"
itunes:title: Donkey of the Day - "Dental Chip"
description:
Today on the show Charlamagne gives "Donkey of the Day" to a couple for damaging a dental office after the husband thinks that they put a microchip in his wife to listen to him.
